/span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Teachout, Terry. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.wsj.com/articles/SB120061524669599113\">\"Funny Man Gets Serious\"</a>. <i><a href=\"/wiki/The_Wall_Street_Journal\" title=\"The Wall Street Journal\">The Wall Street Journal</a></i>. Jan. 18, 2008.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-wapo-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">^ <a href=\"#cite_ref-wapo_8-0\"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-wapo_8-1\"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Marks, Peter. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2010/07/01/AR2010070106215.html\">\"Review: \"New Jerusalem: The Interrogation of Baruch de Spinoza at Theater J\"</a>. <i><a href=\"/wiki/The_Washington_Post\" title=\"The Washington Post\">The Washington Post</a></i>. 2 July 2010.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-9\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-9\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Thielman, Sam. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://variety.com/2008/legit/reviews/new-jerusalem-2-1200553658/\">\"Review: New Jerusalem\"</a>. January 13, 2008. <i><a href=\"/wiki/Variety_(magazine)\" title=\"Variety (magazine)\">Variety</a></i>. </span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-10\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-10\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.huffingtonpost.com/stephen-spotswood/new-jerusalem-interrogation-baruch-de-spinoza_b_1325311.html\">Spotswood, Stephen. Serotsky, Shirley. \"Review: New Jerusalem: The Interrogation of Baruch de Spinoza.\"</a> <i><a href=\"/wiki/The_Huffington_Post\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"The Huffington Post\">The Huffington Post</a></i>. May 9, 2012</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-11\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-11\">^</a></b></span> <sp